- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of technology to assess public mood.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) could be relevant as the paper may discuss the development of software tools for sentiment analysis.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the paper may discuss the interaction between humans and technology in shaping collective emotional perception.
